---
title: Honey Soy-Glazed Chicken Thigh with Creamy Slaw & Sesame Fries
description: We love chicken thighs as they’re full of flavour and stay tender and juicy during cooking. Here, this versatile cut gets
a sticky honey-soy coating that caramelises in the pan. Served next to your new favourite side dish – golden sesame
fries – this meal will keep you coming back for more!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
